## 📋 File Upload Testing Checklist

- [ ] Try uploading .php directly
- [ ] Try double extensions (.php.jpg)
- [ ] Change Content-Type to image/jpeg
- [ ] Add magic bytes to PHP file
- [ ] Try PHP alternatives (.phtml, .phar, .php5)
- [ ] Test null byte injection
- [ ] Check filename for path traversal
- [ ] Upload SVG with XSS payload
- [ ] Try ZIP file with path traversal
- [ ] Check if file is executed or just stored
- [ ] Test .htaccess upload (to override file type handling)
- [ ] Upload web.config on IIS targets

