## 🧠 eWPTXv3 Tips

- Always try **ExifTool** to embed PHP in metadata
- **.htaccess** upload is very effective on Apache
- Look for **file inclusion** after upload (LFI + upload = RCE)
- Test **Content-Disposition** header manipulation
- Try uploading **web.config** on IIS
- Check if app uses **blacklist** (easily bypassed) vs whitelist

